'''麥拉倫MP4-29'''（{{lang-en|McLaren MP4-29}}）是{{le|蒂姆·戈斯|Tim Goss}}所設計的一輛[[麥拉倫車隊|麥拉倫]][[一級方程式賽車|一級方程式賽車]]車型，參賽於[[2014年世界一級方程式錦標賽|2014年世界一級方程式錦標賽]]。<ref name="launch">{{cite news|title=McLaren reveals new F1 car launch date|url=http://www.autosport.com/news/report.php/id/112049|first=Jonathan|last=Noble|work=Autosport|publisher=Jonathan Noble|date=2014-01-07|accessdate=2014-01-07|archive-date=2017-03-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170331183637/http://www.autosport.com/news/report.php/id/112049|dead-url=no}}</ref>這輛車於2014年1月24日亮相，<ref name="launch" />由{{F1|2009}}[[F1世界車手冠軍列表|世界冠軍]][[詹森·巴頓|詹森·巴頓]]及贏得2013年[[雷諾方程式3.5系列賽|雷諾方程式3.5系列賽]]冠軍的新人[[凱文·馬格努森|凱文·馬格努森]]駕駛。<ref name="Magnussen"/><ref name="Button"/>MP4-29被設計來採用[[梅賽德斯車隊|梅賽德斯]]新的1.6升V6渦輪增壓引擎PU106A Hybrid。<ref>{{cite news|title=McLaren believes switch to Honda engines will not compromise 2014|url=http://www.autosport.com/news/report.php/id/107447|first=Jonathan|last=Noble|work=Autosport.com|publisher=Haymarket Publications|date=2013-05-16|accessdate=2013-05-17|quote=McLaren believes its world championship challenge with Mercedes next year will not be compromised by its planned switch to Honda engines for 2015.|archive-date=2019-08-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190808034418/https://www.autosport.com/f1/news/107447/honda-switch-wont-hurt-2014--mclaren|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="PU106A"/>

MP4-29是繼{{le|1988年世界一級方程式錦標賽|1988 Formula One season|1988年}}由[[艾爾頓·冼拿|艾爾頓·冼拿]]及[[亞倫·保魯斯|亞倫·保魯斯]]駕駛，在16場比賽中拿下15場勝利及15次桿位的[[本田車隊|本田]]引擎{{le|麥拉倫MP4/4|McLaren MP4/4|MP4/4}}後，麥拉倫的首輛渦輪動力一級方程式賽車車型。<ref>{{cite news|title=McLaren MP4-29 Mercedes|url=http://www.f1technical.net/f1db/cars/1012/mclaren-mp4-29|work=F1Technical.net|accessdate=2015-01-27|archive-date=2015-02-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150215081808/http://www.f1technical.net/f1db/cars/1012/mclaren-mp4-29|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=McLaren unveil MP4-29 car for 2014 Formula 1 season|url=http://www.bbc.com/sport/0/formula1/25858643|first=Andrew|last=Benson|work=[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]|publisher=[[BBC|BBC]]|date=2014-01-24|accessdate=2015-01-27|archive-date=2015-10-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151017220637/http://www.bbc.com/sport/0/formula1/25858643|dead-url=no}}</ref>這輛車也是最後一輛使用梅賽德斯引擎動力的麥拉倫車型。

==賽季==
[[凱文·馬格努森|凱文·馬格努森]]和[[詹森·巴頓|詹森·巴頓]]於{{F1 GP|2014|澳大利亞}}分別以第三及第四名完賽，但因[[丹尼爾·里卡多|丹尼爾·里卡多]]的失格而晉升至第二與第三名。<ref name="Dan DQ">{{cite news|title=Red Bull's Daniel Ricciardo disqualified from the results of the Australian GP|url=http://www1.skysports.com/f1/news/24239/9216794/red-bulls-daniel-ricciardo-disqualified-from-the-results-of-the-australian-gp|accessdate=2014-03-16|newspaper=Skysports F1|archive-date=2014-10-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141018131110/http://www1.skysports.com/f1/news/24239/9216794/red-bulls-daniel-ricciardo-disqualified-from-the-results-of-the-australian-gp|dead-url=no}}</ref>這輛車也在此站貼上美孚1號塗裝，以紀念該隊與此品牌的20年合作關係。<ref>{{cite news|title=Mobil 1 and McLaren Celebrate 20-Year Partnership in Formula 1|url=http://www.mclaren.com/formula1/partners/Mobil1/mobil-1-and-mclaren-celebrate-20-year-partnership-formula-1/|accessdate=2015-01-27|work=mclaren.com|publisher=[[McLaren|McLaren]]|date=2014-03-13|archive-date=2015-02-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150219063012/http://www.mclaren.com/formula1/partners/Mobil1/mobil-1-and-mclaren-celebrate-20-year-partnership-formula-1/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

在之後幾站的表現並未如澳大利亞一般優異，兩輛車在{{F1 GP|2014|巴林}}雙雙因技術問題而未能完賽。<ref>{{cite news|title=Bahrain Grand Prix Race Report|url=http://www.mclaren.com/formula1/2014/bahrain-grand-prix/Bahrain-grand-prix-race-report_2/|work=mclaren.com|publisher=[[McLaren|McLaren]]|date=2014-04-06|accessdate=2015-01-27|archive-date=2015-04-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150402084909/http://www.mclaren.com/formula1/2014/bahrain-grand-prix/Bahrain-grand-prix-race-report_2/|dead-url=no}}</ref>車隊在整個賽季未能再贏得任何一次頒獎台完賽，雖然在統計上MP4-29是本季最具機械可靠性的車輛，在38次中共有36次符合資格完賽，但他們最終在製造商積分榜上僅取得第五名。

==MP4-29H/1X1==
該隊在與[[本田技研工業|本田]]於{{F1|2015}}展開合作關係前，推出了一輛MP4-29的變型'''McLaren MP4-29H/1X1'''。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.f1fanatic.co.uk/2014/11/25/first-mclaren-honda-test-went-well-boullier/|title=First McLaren-Honda test "went well", says Boullier|first=Keith|last=Collantine|work=F1 Fanatic|publisher=Keith Collantine|date=2014-11-25|accessdate=2014-11-25|archive-date=2014-11-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141127200042/http://www.f1fanatic.co.uk/2014/11/25/first-mclaren-honda-test-went-well-boullier/|dead-url=yes}}</ref>在[[銀石賽道|銀石]]完成試車後，麥拉倫在{{F1 GP|2014|阿布達比}}後一周於[[亞斯碼頭賽道|亞斯碼頭賽道]]的季前測試出動這輛MP4-29H，由麥拉倫的開發車手[[斯托弗·范多恩|斯托弗·范多恩]]駕駛。<ref>{{cite news|title=McLaren to use B-spec car in Abu Dhabi|url=http://www1.skysports.com/f1/report/12479/9559195/mclaren-to-run-b-car-in-abu-dhabi|publisher=[[Sky_Sports|Sky Sports]]|date=2014-11-10|accessdate=2014-11-10|archive-date=2014-11-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141110211813/http://www1.skysports.com/f1/report/12479/9559195/mclaren-to-run-b-car-in-abu-dhabi|dead-url=no}}</ref>這輛車存在著許多問題，在兩天的測試中僅完成了六趟未計時圈。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.formula1.com/news/headlines/2014/11/16696.html|title=Bottas puts Williams on top in Abu Dhabi test|work=Formula1.com|publisher=[[Formula_One_Group|Formula One Administration]]|date=2014-11-25|accessdate=2014-12-15|archive-date=2014-12-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141216020241/http://www.formula1.com/news/headlines/2014/11/16696.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.formula1.com/news/headlines/2014/11/16698.html|title=Wehrlein fastest for Mercedes as Abu Dhabi test ends|work=Formula1.com|publisher=[[Formula_One_Group|Formula One Administration]]|date=2014-11-26|accessdate=2014-12-15|archive-date=2014-12-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141216014721/http://www.formula1.com/news/headlines/2014/11/16698.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

